bles observed in other contexts such as galaxy\nclusters may be formed by winds rather than jets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 May 2015 06:35:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Aug 2015 09:10:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-23"}
