ting from different field\nconfigurations and strengths may have observable consequences for disturbances\npropagating through a stationary recollimation shock.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 May 2015 09:39:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Jun 2015 11:28:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-03"}
