e ratio regimes, which provide useful insights into the\nimpact of the system parameters on the ergodic capacity. Finally, our proposed\nresults are validated via Monte-Carlo simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 May 2015 11:06:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-18"}
