iptic theory on noncommutative tori. A\nnoteworthy technical feature is that we systematize the computation of the\nresolvent expansion for elliptic differential operators on noncommutative tori\nto an extent which makes the (previously employed) computer assistance\nunnecessary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 May 2015 11:39:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Jul 2016 15:36:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-10"}
